Demonstrates a simple state machine and auxiliary functions to dynamically
create a lookup table used to count occurrences of different parts of speech.

Source code from "lex & yacc, 2nd Edition" by John Levine, Tony Mason, Doug
Brown. Copyright 1992 O'Reilly Media, Inc.
ISBN-10: 1-565-92000-7
ISBN-13: 978-1-565-92000-2
